data.description: Welcome to 122 Hoffman! Totally redone from top to bottom in 2017! This meticulously maintained 2 bed, 2 FULL baths home with a FINISHED basement, is ready for you! Located on a quiet street in Pennsport, South Philadelphia, this home will not disappoint. Enter into a light-filled, open floor plan with hardwood floors throughout and an exposed brick wall. A nice space for living room and dining room furniture. This leads to the kitchen that was extended to include plenty of cabinet space and a large eat-in island for additional seating. Head out back to 1 of THREE outdoor spaces. Upstairs will welcome you to the bedroom #1 with custom closets and a balcony that leads to an additional roof deck with some of the best views of the city! Upstairs also includes a full bath with beautiful shower, jacuzzi tub and double vanity! The second bedroom has tons of natural light and another custom closet for plenty of storage. Don't forget the convenient 2nd floor laundry! Need more space?? Head to the FINISHED basement with an additional full bathroom. This home is located 1/2 block from a FREE PUBLIC PARKING LOT located under the 95 highway. Don't drive? Take 5 minute walk to Target, Acme supermarket, and anything else you may need within Snyder Plaza. A 5-minute drive to Ikea, Walmart, Giant Supermarket and so much more. Several cool restaurants such as Mifflin Tavern, Moonshine, and several cafes. Hop on I-95 highway within minutes, 10 minutes from the sports stadiums. Schedule your showings today!
